{"id":1687683,"retrievedAt":"2026-05-04T12:41:30.943Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1687683,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"In The Present Tense","overview":"What is an ethnographic film? Can there even be one? This film is an attempt, or as we keep calling it our \"botched baby\" as we try to capture and read Humayunpur in Delhi following the question— how is the city reproduced by the northeast migrants in Delhi? The title is play on words, for the tension and violence that is omnipresent in this process of place-making often goes unnoticed by the rice beer-paglus who haunt the lanes of Humayunpur. The film takes you through a whole day in the place, from morning when the shops and stores are still setting up till night when the eyes gloss over the bright signboards and lights. Somewhere in all of this there is an ethnographic spirit, or at least an attempt...","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/oTDsfmlpujPMa6b31xI8x2Yelop.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"","revenue":0,"runtime":11,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"An Ethnographic Fillum","title":"In The Present Tense","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"external_ids":{"imdb_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"instagram_id":null,"twitter_id":null},"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6187493,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Neel","original_name":"Neel","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"69f7de304c670b81dfa0ac17","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6187494,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Lynx","original_name":"Lynx","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"69f7de55b8851b3dfa50910d","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"gender